e":"2017-12-13T15:11:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁睇佢教果幾年既巴塞係歐聯真係年年都有黑哨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n永遠關鍵時刻就會黑鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地球聯合軍就係咁黎，但班巴迷覺得人地係打唔贏先反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n疤狗真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n相隔5年巴迷紛紛上水吹奏巴塞同美斯既豐功偉績，真係當人唔記得六冠嗰年北京電視機架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a8a21aa6a42210fb32501af99731c59c2d0369","tid":498131,"uid":27961,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:13:59.000Z","msg":"唔係最勁<br />\n<br />\n但都比大部分領隊好"},{"pid":"c4c0ffa7b3b2a67411953696a10a23a6b0622fae","tid":498131,"uid":10176,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:16:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係最勁<br />\n<br />\n但都比大部分領隊好</blockquote><br />\n最勁梗係雲爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be30ecbd0808f43b4daeeb3f57fc33aec2273684","tid":498131,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:17:36.000Z","msg":"見好就收啦你班仆街<br />\n我唔想鏝城同哥狗比你地吹奏到失冠"},{"pid":"2c29443a8616fbbb059cacfd06a9e90766be7c97","tid":498131,"uid":119729,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:17:43.000Z","msg":"唔講成績 費事罵戰<br />\n<br />\n不過佢真係令好多球員進步<br />\n美斯 布斯基斯 柏度 沙維<br />\n<br />\n尤其後2位 無左哥帥戰鬥力大打折扣"},{"pid":"7e8e411c2bd2be00a069f4ce782828bcf77e5b4f","tid":498131,"uid":993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:24:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見好就收啦你班仆街<br />\n我唔想鏝城同哥狗比你地吹奏到失冠</blockquote><br />\n講撚到呢到有好大影響力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2010af3fbeefe903e07960d0483daecf6a78da41","tid":498131,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s